		           <td width="650" align="left" class="RegText" valign="top">	
				      <p><strong>Title:</strong> Director of Parks and Recreation

<br>
					  <strong>Phone:</strong> 708-361-1807<br>
					  <strong>E-mail:</strong> <a href="mailto:recdept@palosheights.org">recdept@palosheights.org
